import React,{useState} from "react"
import { useNavigate } from "react-router";

    Flex,
    Stack,
    VStack,
    Text,
    FormControl,
    FormLabel,
    Input,
    InputGroup,
    InputLeftElement,
    Link,
    Button,
    Textarea
} from "@chakra-ui/react";

import{
    ArrowRightIcon,
    LockIcon,
} from "@chakra-ui/icons"

const Diary=()=>{
 
    return(
        <Flex 
          direction="column"
          w="100vw"
          h="100vh"
          align="center"
          justify="center"
          p={10}
          bgGradient="linear(360deg, #232A33 ,black)"
        >
            <Textarea
                w="full"
                h="70%"

                focusBorderColor="#292C2D"
                boxShadow="0px 0px 3px whiteAlpha.500"
                fontSize="2xl"
                textColor="white"
                resize="none"
            />

            <Button
             bgGradient="radial(#3DB1AB,#0E1515)"
             _hover={{bg:"radial(red,#0E1515)"}}
             mt={5}
             w="50%"
             h="20%"
            >
                <Text
                fontSize="3xl"
                textColor="black"
                >

                </Text>

            </Button>
          

        </Flex>
    )
}

export default Diary;
